      "name": "Relative hemolysis index validation against FDA pump experimental data",
      "description": "CFD-predicted relative hemolysis index (RH) compared against experimental measurements from the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump benchmark. RH < 1 criterion satisfied across all 5 flow-speed operating points. Mean absolute error 8.3%, within acceptable bounds for MRL 2."
