      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence monitoring sufficient at MRL 2; formal solver error quantification not required.",
      "rationale": "Residual convergence to 1e-5 monitored for all equations. Mass imbalance < 0.01% confirmed for all simulations. Formal numerical solver error quantification beyond convergence monitoring is not required at MRL 2 and has not been performed."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 1,
      "achievedLevel": 1,
      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Peer review of simulation setup sufficient at MRL 2.",
      "rationale": "Simulation setup reviewed by a second qualified CFD engineer. Boundary condition assignments, turbulence model selection (SST k-omega), and hemolysis model implementation confirmed correct. Formal use error analysis not required at MRL 2."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model form",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Governing equations and constitutive models must be appropriate for the physics of interest; turbulence model selection must be justified.",
      "rationale": "Incompressible Reynolds-Averaged Navier-Stokes equations with SST k-omega turbulence closure selected. Blood treated as Newtonian fluid (shear rate > 100 1/s throughout pump domain, Newtonian assumption valid). Giersiepen-Wurzinger hemolysis model applied via Lagrangian particle tracking. Model form appropriate for MRL 2 CPB hemolysis prediction."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Model inputs",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 2,
