      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "All model inputs must be documented with sources; blood rheological properties must be from published literature or measured values.",
      "rationale": "Blood density 1060 kg/m3 and dynamic viscosity 0.0035 Pa·s sourced from published literature (Merrill et al.). Pump geometry from FDA benchmark CAD files. Inlet velocity profiles derived from experimental flow rate measurements. All inputs documented in simulation log with traceability to source data."
    },
